documentation:
A plugin that provides HTTP functionality.

Usage:
    kernel.add_plugin(HttpPlugin(), "http")

Examples:
    {{http.getAsync $url}}
    {{http.postAsync $url}}
    {{http.putAsync $url}}
    {{http.deleteAsync $url}}

